# Playwright Tests

This repository contains automated tests using Playwright for [Localizify](https://localizify.com/).

## Description

The project aims to deeper understanding how to use Playwright in different types of testing.

## Installation

To install and set up the project locally, follow these steps:

1. **Clone the repository**
git clone https://github.com/Paul-Mongoose/makarenko-playwright-tests.git
cd makarenko-playwright-tests

2.**Install dependencies**
npm install

3.**Run tests**
npm test

4.***Project Structure***
helpers/: Contains interfaces and test data
tests/: Contains all the test files.
utils/: Contains functions and other stuff
playwright.config.ts: Configuration file for Playwright.
package.json: Project dependencies and scripts.

5.**Authors**
   Pavlo Makarenko - https://github.com/Paul-Mongoose
